-- Permira not interested in buying RWE: source
-- 
-- Thu May 29, 2008 8:11am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/05/29/us-rwe-permira-idUSWEA835420080529

 

 FRANKFURT  (Reuters) - Private equity firm Permira PERM.UL has no interest in buying German utility RWE ( RWEG.DE ), a source familiar with the matter told Reuters on Thursday. 

 Permira declined to comment. (Reporting by  Philipp Halstrick )